version.diff:
```diff
+ --delete added to bot, use the flag to delete the command message!
+ Text Command added!
+ RacPlay functionality added! Bot will now play music in current channel the user is in
- Removed ability to change status from commands (terminal only)
- Bot will sometimes start typing continuously, there is no timeout function for this, but one is coming.
+ TTS support (global config.js file)
- When searching, only grabs first result.
```

help:
```yaml
help		# Display This Message
search		# Search for sounds / music
RacPlay		# Search term, and play result!
stop		# Stops current playback
--delete		# Delete that message
version		# Sends version information
uptime		# Show uptime of Bot in seconds.
thanks		# thank the bot
ping		# Ping the bot
freakout		# Bot will freakout
text		# Bot will respond with large bold text```
